album.title: You Could Have It So Much Better

wiki.content: "Walk Away" is the second single from Franz Ferdinand's second album, You Could Have It So Much Better. The release date of the single is 5 December 2005. The song's melody line is borrowed from Kraftwerk's "The Model", or in German, "Das Modell". This is particularly clear in the opening of the song.
